  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large pot, heat oil over medium heat.",
    "2. Add onion and garlic, cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "3. Add turkey neck pieces and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "4. Add Ethiopian spices, water, and wot spice mix.",
    "5. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "6. Add diced tomato and cook for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "7. Season with salt to taste.",
    "8. Serve hot with injera or rice."
